---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="2026年中国投资思路：百年变局、大周期转换与未来方向">

<style>
  /* ── typography ── */
  .report-body { max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; }

  .report-h1 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 2.1rem; line-height: 1.25; color: #111; }
  .report-h2 { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.45rem; color: #0B2C56; margin: 3rem 0 1rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 2px solid #e5e0d8; }
  .report-h3 { font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.05rem; color: #1a1a1a; margin: 2rem 0 0.6rem; }
  .report-p  { color: #3a3630; line-height: 1.9; margin: 0.9rem 0; font-size: 0.9375rem; }
  .report-lead { font-size: 1.0625rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.85; }
  .report-body strong { color: #111; }

  /* ── hero ── */
  .china-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 72vh;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: flex-end;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(170deg, rgba(60,10,10,0.88) 0%, rgba(120,25,25,0.78) 40%, rgba(10,20,45,0.82) 100%),
      url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1508804052814-cd3ba865a116?auto=format&fit=crop&w=2560&q=95');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center 35%;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .china-hero::after {
    content:'';
    position: absolute; inset: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 60% 30%, rgba(180,40,40,0.25) 0%, transparent 65%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* ── stat cards ── */
  .stat-bar { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px,1fr)); gap: 1px; background: #e5e0d8; }
  .stat-item { background: #fff; padding: 1.2rem 1.4rem; }
  .stat-num  { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.6rem; font-weight: 700; color: #0B2C56; line-height: 1; }
  .stat-label{ font-size: 0.72rem; color: #888; margin-top: 0.3rem; line-height: 1.35; }

  /* ── toc ── */
  .toc { background: #f5f3ef; border: 1px solid #e5e0d8; border-radius: 14px; padding: 1.5rem 1.8rem; }
  .toc-title { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #aaa; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .toc a { display: block; font-size: 0.85rem; color: #555; text-decoration: none; padding: 0.28rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid transparent; transition: color .2s; }
  .toc a:hover { color: #0B2C56; }
  .toc-num { color: #B8860B; font-weight: 600; min-width: 1.8rem; display: inline-block; }

  /* ── callout boxes ── */
  .callout       { border-left: 4px solid #5B9BD5; background: #f0f6ff; border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0; padding: 1rem 1.3rem; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
  .callout-gold  { border-left-color: #B8860B; background: #fdf9ee; }
  .callout-red   { border-left-color: #c0392b; background: #fff2f0; }
  .callout-green { border-left-color: #27ae60; background: #f0faf4; }
  .callout p     { margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; color: #333; line-height: 1.7; }
  .callout strong{ color: #0B2C56; }
  .callout-gold strong { color: #8B6914; }
  .callout-red strong  { color: #922B21; }

  /* ── data tables ── */
  .report-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.83rem; margin: 1.2rem 0; }
  .report-table th { background: #0B2C56; color: #fff; padding: 0.6rem 0.8rem; text-align: left; font-weight: 600; }
  .report-table td { padding: 0.55rem 0.8rem; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; color: #333; vertical-align: top; line-height: 1.55; }
  .report-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .report-table tr:nth-child(even) td { background: #fafaf8; }
  .report-table .star { color: #B8860B; font-weight: 700; }
  .report-table .hi   { color: #c0392b; font-weight: 600; }
  .report-table .pos  { color: #27ae60; font-weight: 600; }

  /* ── matrix grid ── */
  .matrix { display: grid; grid-template-columns: auto 1fr 1fr; gap: 2px; font-size: 0.8rem; margin: 1.2rem 0; }
  .matrix-label { background: #0B2C56; color: #fff; padding: 0.5rem 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; writing-mode: vertical-rl; text-orientation: mixed; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 0.72rem; }
  .matrix-header { background: #1a3a6b; color: #fff; padding: 0.5rem 0.8rem; text-align: center; font-weight: 600; border-radius: 4px; }
  .matrix-cell { padding: 0.9rem 1rem; border-radius: 4px; }
  .matrix-s5 { background: #fef3cd; border: 1px solid #f0c040; }
  .matrix-s4 { background: #e8f3fc; border: 1px solid #93c8e0; }
  .matrix-s3 { background: #f0faf4; border: 1px solid #7ed9a0; }
  .matrix-s2 { background: #fff8f0; border: 1px solid #f0b070; }
  .matrix-cell .stars { font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: 0.3rem; }
  .matrix-cell .tag   { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.78rem; color: #333; }
  .matrix-cell .items { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin-top: 0.2rem; }

  /* ── section badge ── */
  .section-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    background: #0B2C56; color: #fff;
    padding: 0.25rem 0.85rem; border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.68rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
  }

  /* ── risk list ── */
  .risk-item { display: flex; gap: 1rem; padding: 0.9rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #eee; }
  .risk-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .risk-tag { flex-shrink: 0; background: #fff2f0; color: #c0392b; border: 1px solid #f5c6c0; border-radius: 6px; padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem; font-size: 0.7rem; font-weight: 600; height: fit-content; white-space: nowrap; }
  .risk-text { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.6; }
  .risk-data { font-size: 0.75rem; color: #c0392b; font-weight: 600; margin-top: 0.2rem; }

  /* ── direction cards ── */
  .dir-card { background: #fff; border: 1px solid #e5e0d8; border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.3rem 1.5rem; margin: 1rem 0; }
  .dir-card .dir-num { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #B8860B; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0.4rem; }
  .dir-card h4 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #0B2C56; margin: 0 0 0.6rem; }
  .dir-card p  { font-size: 0.85rem; color: #555; line-height: 1.65; margin: 0; }

  /* ── profit tier ── */
  .profit-tier { border-left: 4px solid; padding: 1rem 1.2rem; margin: 1rem 0; border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0; }
  .tier-high   { border-color: #27ae60; background: #f0faf4; }
  .tier-mid    { border-color: #5B9BD5; background: #f0f6ff; }
  .tier-low    { border-color: #e74c3c; background: #fff2f0; }
  .tier-label  { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.82rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .tier-high .tier-label  { color: #1a7a40; }
  .tier-mid  .tier-label  { color: #1a4e8a; }
  .tier-low  .tier-label  { color: #8B1A1A; }

  /* ── wave transition ── */
  .wave-top { display: block; width: 100%; }
  .wave-bot { display: block; width: 100%; margin-top: -2px; }

  /* ── source list ── */
  .source-list { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 0.5rem; }
  .source-tag  { background: #f5f3ef; border: 1px solid #e5e0d8; border-radius: 6px; padding: 0.25rem 0.7rem; font-size: 0.72rem; color: #666; }

  /* ── career path ── */
  .path-row { display: flex; gap: 0.8rem; padding: 0.7rem 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f0ece5; align-items: flex-start; }
  .path-year { flex-shrink: 0; width: 5.5rem; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; color: #B8860B; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; padding-top: 0.1rem; }
  .path-text { font-size: 0.83rem; color: #444; line-height: 1.6; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .report-h1 { font-size: 1.55rem; }
    .stat-bar { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
    .matrix { font-size: 0.72rem; }
  }
</style>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!--  HERO — Great Wall                          -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="-mx-6 -mt-14 china-hero">

  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="z-index:1;">
    <!-- decorative red circle glow -->
    <div style="position:absolute;top:18%;left:55%;width:420px;height:420px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(200,40,40,0.18),transparent 70%);transform:translate(-50%,-50%);"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative px-6 pb-20 pt-32 max-w-5xl mx-auto w-full" style="z-index:2;">

    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-5">
      <span style="background:rgba(184,134,11,0.25);border:1px solid rgba(184,134,11,0.55);color:#f5d060;font-size:0.68rem;letter-spacing:0.18em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;padding:0.3rem 1rem;border-radius:999px;">
        我的思考 · My Thinking
      </span>
      <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);font-size:0.78rem;">2026-04-08</span>
    </div>

    <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-white mb-5 leading-tight"
        style="font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4.5vw,3.2rem);max-width:680px;text-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
      2026年中国投资思路
    </h1>

    <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.65);font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.75;max-width:520px;margin-bottom:2rem;">
      百年变局、大周期转换与未来方向<br/>
      <span style="font-size:0.9rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">全面分析六条主线 · A股盈利扫描 · 五大投资方向 · AI时代职业路线图</span>
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2" style="font-size:0.82rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">
      <span><span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.75);font-weight:600;">8</span> 个分析部分</span>
      <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">·</span>
      <span>约 15,000 字深度分析</span>
      <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);">·</span>
      <span>数据截至 2026 年 4 月</span>
    </div>

  </div>

  <!-- wave bottom -->
  <svg class="wave-bot" viewBox="0 0 1440 56" preserveAspectRatio="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="z-index:3;position:relative;">
    <path d="M0 56L1440 56L1440 22C1200 50 960 4 720 22C480 40 240 2 0 22L0 56Z" fill="#f8f7f4"/>
  </svg>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!--  STAT BAR                                   -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="bg-[#f8f7f4] px-6 pb-0">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="stat-bar rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-sm border border-[#e5e0d8]">
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">5.0%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">2025 GDP 增速<br/>分季度逐季递减</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">38%</div>
        <div class="stat-label">消费占 GDP 比重<br/>美国为 68%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">8.4万亿</div>
        <div class="stat-label">2025 房产销售额<br/>较峰值腰斩 54%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">$4,325</div>
        <div class="stat-label">2025 金价 / 盎司<br/>全年涨幅 +66%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat-item">
        <div class="stat-num">792万</div>
        <div class="stat-label">2025 年出生人口<br/>历史新低，同比 −17%</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!--  MAIN CONTENT                               -->
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="bg-[#f8f7f4] px-6 py-14">
<div class="report-body">

  <!-- Back link -->
  <a href="/research/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-stone-400 hover:text-columbia-navy text-xs transition-colors no-underline mb-10 group">
    <span class="group-hover:-translate-x-0.5 transition-transform inline-block">←</span>
    返回金融投研
  </a>

  <!-- TOC -->
  <nav class="toc mb-14">
    <p class="toc-title">目录 / Contents</p>
    <div class="space-y-0.5">
      <a href="#part1"><span class="toc-num">一</span>历史坐标——我们正站在什么样的节点</a>
      <a href="#part2"><span class="toc-num">二</span>中国经济发展的六条主线</a>
      <a href="#part3"><span class="toc-num">三</span>六大风险清单（2026 最新数据）</a>
      <a href="#part4"><span class="toc-num">四</span>经济大周期的深层分析</a>
      <a href="#part5"><span class="toc-num">五</span>投资方向的深层逻辑</a>
      <a href="#part6"><span class="toc-num">六</span>A 股行业盈利扫描——钱在往哪里流</a>
      <a href="#part7"><span class="toc-num">七</span>AI 时代的职业方向——文商科的路线图</a>
      <a href="#part8"><span class="toc-num">八</span>总结——一句话和一张图</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <!-- ─────────────────────────────── -->
  <!-- PART 1                          -->
  <!-- ─────────────────────────────── -->
  <div id="part1">
    <div class="section-badge">第一部分</div>
    <h2 class="report-h2" style="border-top:none;padding-top:0;margin-top:0.5rem;">历史坐标——我们正站在什么样的节点</h2>

    <h3 class="report-h3">1.1 百年变局的真正含义：不是隐喻，是结构性现实</h3>
    <p class="report-p">"百年未有之大变局"不是口号。如果你把时间轴拉到 1914 年，会发现今天的世界和当时的结构性相似度极高。</p>

    <div class="callout callout-gold">
      <p><strong>关键历史教训：</strong>1914–1945 年的秩序转换期，是长达 30 年的反复震荡。在这个过程中，旧秩序的受益者（英国、欧洲旧贵族、农业地主）持续丧失财富，而新秩序的建设者（美国工业资本、石油寡头、技术创新者）持续积累财富。<strong>每一次国际秩序重构期，都是旧资产大幅贬值、新资产大幅升值的时期。</strong></p>
    </div>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mt-4 mb-6">
    <table class="report-table">
      <thead><tr>
        <th>维度</th><th>1910–1945</th><th>2020–2040（我们所在的位置）</th>
      </tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>霸权交替</td><td>英国衰落 → 美国崛起</td><td>美国相对衰落 → 中国/多极崛起</td></tr>
        <tr><td>货币体系</td><td>金本位崩塌 → 美元体系建立</td><td>美元主导承压 → 多币种/数字货币/黄金回归</td></tr>
        <tr><td>核心技术</td><td>钢铁、石油、化工、内燃机</td><td>半导体、AI、量子计算、能源转型</td></tr>
        <tr><td>贸易体系</td><td>自由贸易瓦解 → 经济集团化</td><td>WTO碎片化 → 供应链脱钩、关税战</td></tr>
        <tr><td>意识形态</td><td>自由主义 vs 法西斯 vs 共产主义</td><td>自由民主 vs 国家资本主义 vs 民粹主义</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    </div>

    <h3 class="report-h3">1.2 康德拉季耶夫长波：我们在第六波的起点</h3>
    <p class="report-p">经济大周期每 40–60 年经历一轮由重大技术革命驱动的"创造性毁灭"。我们正处在第五波的"冬季"和第六波的"春季"之间。</p>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
    <table class="report-table">
      <thead><tr><th>波次</th><th>时期</th><th>核心技术</th><th>代表性财富形态</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>第一波</td><td>1780–1840</td><td>纺织机械、水力</td><td>英国纺织厂主</td></tr>
        <tr><td>第三波</td><td>1890–1940</td><td>电力、化工、内燃机</td><td>石油寡头、汽车工业</td></tr>
        <tr><td>第五波</td><td>1990–2020</td><td>互联网、移动通信、ICT</td><td>硅谷科技巨头、平台经济</td></tr>
        <tr style="background:#fffbe6;"><td class="star">第六波 ★</td><td class="star">2020–2060?</td><td class="star">AI、清洁能源、生物技术、机器人</td><td class="star">正在形成中…</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    </div>

    <div class="callout mt-4">
      <p><strong>中国竞逐第六波的三张底牌：</strong>① 硬制造底座——全球唯一起跑即完备的机电软硬件一体化供应链；② 能源基建——光伏、风电、储能网络已为第六波囤积最廉价的能源；③ 海量复杂场景——世界工厂+高密度城市，为 AI 进入物理世界提供独一无二的训练道场。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="callout callout-red mt-3">
      <p><strong>三大生死考验：</strong>① 制度能不能给创新让路？② 资本能不能流向真正有生产率的方向？③ 人才能不能被激活而不是被内卷消耗？——2024 年国考报名 <strong>303 万人</strong>，录取比约 77:1，这是一场极端的智力错配。</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ─────────────────────────────── -->
  <!-- PART 2                          -->
  <!-- ─────────────────────────────── -->
  <div id="part2">
    <div class="section-badge mt-10">第二部分</div>
    <h2 class="report-h2" style="border-top:none;padding-top:0;margin-top:0.5rem;">中国经济发展的六条主线</h2>

    <h3 class="report-h3">主线一：从投资拉动转向消费拉动</h3>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-4">
    <table class="report-table">
      <thead><tr><th>维度</th><th>数据</th><th>解读</th></tr></thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>2025 年 GDP</td><td class="hi">140.19 万亿，同比 +5.0%</td><td>分季度逐季递减：5.4→5.2→4.8→4.5</td></tr>
        <tr><td>消费占 GDP</td><td class="hi">约 38%</td><td>美国 68%、德国 52%、日本 55%</td></tr>
        <tr><td>居民储蓄率</td><td class="hi">33–35%</td><td>美国约 5%，全球极端值</td></tr>
        <tr><td>2026 刺激包</td><td>1000 亿 + 2500 亿超长期特别国债</td><td>合计仅占社零 0.7%</td></tr>
        <tr><td>IMF 2026 预测</td><td>4.5%（上调 0.3pp）</td><td>中期 2030 年降至约 3.5%</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    </div>

    <div class="callout callout-gold">
      <p><strong>核心判断：</strong>5% 是政策硬撑的结果，不是市场自发均衡。消费修复的真正拐点在家庭资产负债表，不在刺激政策。房价止跌（预计 2027 年企稳）→ 储蓄率拐头（每降 1pp 释放约 1.4 万亿增量）→ 就业改善，三个先决条件缺一不可。<strong>这是一个 5–15 年的结构性过程。</strong></p>
    </div>

    <h3 class="report-h3">主线二：房地产完成功能转型</h3>
    <p class="report-p">2025 年商品房销售额约 <strong>8.4 万亿元</strong>，仅为 2021 年峰值（18.2 万亿元）的 <strong>46%</strong>。S&P 预测 2026 年再降 6–7%，房价再跌 1.5–2.5%，反弹可能要到 <strong>2027 年</strong>。</p>
    <div class="callout callout-red">
